column7: NSLOCTEXT("(2BD69ABFFCA7A1065CE4567534E00EFE)", "75CFDE9C4754FF34F106178ED3D13EFA", "You are able to rest here safely, with a base cost of a Ration for outside the village walls. The village\'s elder approaches, saying,“We’re open to trade, so don’t be afraid to stop by.We have to eat too, you know, and you’re a lot of folks.”")
